On this day for Blogger

INTRODUCTION
============

  This is a Blogger plugin. It lists posts which have same calendar date in
  recent years.

RELATED LINKS
=============

  * Project's website : http://code.google.com/p/blogger-otd/
  * Get Support       : http://groups.google.com/group/otd-for-blogger
  * Code Generator    : http://www.livibetter.com/page/onthisday.htm
  * Author's website  : http://www.livibetter.com/

CREDITS
=======

  * jquery
  * Google AJAX Feed API

